cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on depth estimation and completion using high-resolution depth measurements, which is a core topic in computer vision. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper evaluates the robustness of depth sensing methods in different driving conditions, which is relevant to robotics and autonomous driving. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as machine learning methods are often used in depth estimation and completion. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as AI techniques are used in computer vision and robotics. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with high-resolution depth measurements, which is relevant to computer graphics.
